  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To collect information on pediatric patients receiving Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy
      (CRT) with permanent biventricular pacing (BVP) as a method of treating chronic heart
      failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
